    "**Exercise 1.**\n",
    "\n",
    "Consider a window with width 1000px and height 800px with a viewport whose opposite corners, in pixels, are (200,100) and (800,700).\n",
    "\n",
    "Give the viewport matrix which transforms normalized device coordinates to this viewport."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$\n",
