    "0                       & 0                     & 1⁡\n",
    "\\end{array}\\right]\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "Let $M_1 = TR$ and $M_2 = RT$ be two transformation matrices. Consider the line segment defined by $v_1 = (0,0)$ and $v_2 = (2,1)$. Draw the line segment when transformed by $M_1$ and when transformed by $M_2$. Describe, in words, what is the difference between the affine transforms $M_1$ and $M_2$? Why is the result different?\n",
    "\n",
    "$ M_1 =\n",
