    "(0)(\\cos\\left(30\\right)) + (1)(\\sin\\left(30\\right)) + (3)(0)        & (0)(−\\sin\\left(30\\right)) + (1)(\\cos\\left(30\\right)) + (3)(0)      & (0)(0) + (1)(0) + (3)(1) \\\\\n",
    "(0)(\\cos\\left(30\\right)) + (0)(\\sin\\left(30\\right)) + (1)(0)        & (0)(−\\sin\\left(30\\right)) + (0)(\\cos\\left(30\\right)) + (1)(0)      & (0)(0) + (0)(0) + (1)(1)\n",
    "\\end{array}\\right]\n",
    "$\n",
    "\n",
    "$ =\n",
    "\\left[\\begin{array}{ccc}\n",
